question: Give me all Danish movies.

question: To which countries does the Himalayan mountain system extend?

question: What is the largest country in the world?
dbpedia_query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Country ; dbo:areaTotal ?n } ORDER BY DESC(?n) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
